@atonemo.electronics and @nts_radio have teamed up on the NTS Radio Player, a compact Wi-Fi streamer that brings NTS’s curated channels and infinite mixtapes to almost any speaker or amplifier.⁠
⁠
The player supports hi-res audio up to 24-bit/192kHz, plus AirPlay 2, and  built for anyone who misses discovering music by accident, without needing to scroll, search, or overthink what to play next.⁠

